<item>
            <title>[SPR-5359] Collection (List) backed form fields bound via &lt;form:checkbox&gt; or  &lt;form:radiobutton&gt; generate invalid HTML id attribute</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-5359</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HTML code generated via Spring&apos;s form tag library for checkboxes and radiobuttons is generating invalid HTML id attributes (square brackets to represent array).  This appears to work fine for the other form input types, but the HTML is incorrect for checkboxes and radiobuttons.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sample code:&lt;br/&gt;
---------------&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;c:forEach var=&quot;currentTest&quot; items=&quot;$&lt;/p&gt;
{testForm.tests}
&lt;p&gt;&quot; varStatus=&quot;itStatus&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;li&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;form:checkbox path=&quot;tests[$&lt;/p&gt;
{itStatus.index}
&lt;p&gt;].copy&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;/li&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/c:forEach&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
---------------&lt;br/&gt;
Generates the following HTML for the checkbox:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;input id=&quot;tests&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.copy1&quot; name=&quot;tests&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.copy&quot; type=&quot;checkbox&quot; value=&quot;true&quot;/&amp;gt;&amp;lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; name=&quot;_tests&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.copy&quot; value=&quot;on&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Changing the form:checkbox tag to a form:hidden tag renders valid HTML:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;input id=&quot;tests0.copy&quot; name=&quot;tests&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;.copy&quot; type=&quot;hidden&quot; value=&quot;false&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;p&gt;This appears to be related to this issue: &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.springframework.org/browse/SPR-2380?&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://jira.springframework.org/browse/SPR-2380?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
